{"tid":1283853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係「試著說我無野講」原post，我有野想講","createTime":"2019-07-04T02:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T10:16:50.000Z","uid":114801,"like":161,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1ef77b36022d8fbc4df4ab2a6ffa07c0cb174d58","tid":1283853,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:45:40.000Z","msg":"不要說「推」或「push」，試著說「我無野講」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1282588\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1282588</a><br />\n<br />\n做之前諗一諗，唔好貪得意跟風，甚至洗版。<br />\n<br />\n1. 你覆「我無野講」之前，係唔係本身都想留個「推」字？<br />\n<br />\n2. 睇場合，例如情緒/負能量post，你以前都唔會入去留個「推」字就走啦。<br />\n<br />\n3. 睇主題，高質資訊post不妨一推，但討論post請盡量討論。<br />\n<br />\n「我無野講」係一個拯救義士既idea，廢物利用本身都無咩意義既「推」字，透過不斷重覆，將「我無野講」呢個概念帶入深層記憶，讓經驗不足既巴絲打面對狗隻威逼時可以更容易堅持「我無野講」<br />\n<br />\n在連登上，無論咩議題，文宣又好、發夢又好，懇請大家一定要盡量多參與討論，deep learning式社運先會學得快，學得有效率。<br />\n最後，提下大家，我地輸緊7-0，不過最後一定會贏，仲要齊上齊落一齊贏"},{"pid":"798b1bc5aa54b79e71d7739446b922d59c85f25c","tid":1283853,"uid":86509,"like":44,"dislike":3,"score":41,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:49:20.000Z","msg":"而家發展到用簽名檔又點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mPbOe1G.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmPbOe1G.gif&h=a2c4327c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a00862b392d3747fefe50a897726773bee82fe1","tid":1283853,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:51:51.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"f0bd2dd299045ca89797f73dd81a59423d440922","tid":1283853,"uid":100143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:53:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d7bab85e03371726bbbb9abf006f414e86ccb0b","tid":1283853,"uid":20602,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"798b1bc5aa54b79e71d7739446b922d59c85f25c","tid":1283853,"uid":86509,"like":44,"dislike":3,"score":41,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:49:20.000Z","msg":"而家發展到用簽名檔又點睇<img s